"Se quere usar <application>PGP</application> ou <application>GnuPG</"
"application>, pode configurar as súas chaves &openpgp; e/ou certificados "
"&smime; na lapela <link linkend=\"configure-identity-cryptography"
"\"><guilabel>Criptografía</guilabel></link>."

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Advanced</guilabel> and <guilabel>Templates</guilabel> tabs "
"can be used to tailor the way outgoing messages from this identity will be "
"formatted and processed. See <link linkend=\"configure-generalinfo"
"\">Configure &kmail;</link> for more detailed instructions."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:267
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Optionally, go to the <guilabel>Signature</guilabel> tab and enter your "
#| "signature. This is a short text that will be automatically appended to "
#| "all your messages. It has nothing to do with <emphasis>digital "
#| "signatures</emphasis>."
msgid ""
"Optionally, go to the <guilabel>Signature</guilabel> tab and enter your "
"signature. This is a short bit of verbiage that will be automatically "
"appended to all your messages. It has nothing to do with <emphasis>digital "
"signatures</emphasis>. You may also wish to insert a small personal avatar "
"in outgoing message headers via the <guilabel>Picture</guilabel> tab."
msgstr ""
"Opcionalmente, vaia á lapela <guilabel>Sinatura</guilabel> e insira a súa "
"sinatura. Este é un texto curto que se engadirá automaticamente a todas as "
"súas mensaxes. Non ten nada a ver coas <emphasis>sinaturas dixitais</"
"emphasis>."

#. Tag: title
#: getting-started.docbook:280
#, no-c-format
msgid "Setting up your Account"
msgstr "Configurar a Sua Conta"

#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:282
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The <guilabel>Network</guilabel> page contains the settings that tell "
#| "&kmail; how to send and receive your email messages. Many of these "
#| "settings can vary greatly depending on the setup of your system and on "
#| "the kind of network that your mail server is located in. If you do not "
#| "know what setting to choose or what to put in a field, consult your "
#| "Internet Service Provider (<acronym>ISP</acronym>) or system "
#| "administrator."
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Accounts</guilabel> page also contains the settings that tell "
"&kmail; how to send and receive your email messages. Many of these settings "
"can vary greatly depending on the way your system is set up, and on the kind "
"of network in which your mail server is located. If you do not know what "
"setting to choose or what to put in a field, consult your <acronym>ISP</"
"acronym> (Internet Service Provider) or system administrator."
msgstr ""
"A páxina <guilabel>Rede</guilabel> contén as opcións que lle din ao &kmail; "
"como enviar e recibir as mensaxes de correo. Moitas destas opcións poderán "
"depender en grande medida da configuración do sistema e do tipo de rede no "
"que se localiza o servidor de correo. Se non sabe que configuración escoller "
"ou o que pór nun campo, consulte co seu Fornecedor de Acceso a Internet "
"(<acronym>ISP</acronym>) ou administrador de sistemas."

