#. Tag: para
#: getting-started.docbook:394
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You will then be presented with the <guilabel>Add account</guilabel> "
#| "window. First, fill in the <guilabel>Name</guilabel> field to name your "
#| "account. You can choose any name you like. <guilabel>Login</guilabel>, "
#| "<guilabel>Password</guilabel>, and <guilabel>Host</guilabel> should be "
#| "filled in with the appropriate information from your <acronym>ISP</"
